				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Verse of Vesagran <a name="67832"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 22 04 2:51 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>What the song do is reducing an incomming hit by 5% to a cumulate total of 450.
<br />

<br />
Example:
<br />
mobs hit you:
<br />
867
<br />
845
<br />
1276
<br />
987
<br />
1186
<br />

<br />
(867 * 0.05) + (845 * 0.05) + (1276 * 0.05) + (987 * 0.05) + (1186 * 0.05) = 258 damage absorbed.
<br />

<br />
In another words, you need to receive 9000 damage to absorb the full 450hp the song provide.
<br />

<br />
Thats how I understood song.
<br />
</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
