				<td colspan="2"><span>Such a fine line between a crap song and an overpowered one.  I am thinking that Sony has learned from the past PoP experience that gave us perhaps too much in one expansion...later leading to some nerfs and not much more in the newer expansions.
<br />

<br />
If they had made this song worth twisting, it would be in the lineup 100% of the time nearly.  Just as the current line up is really only about 6 core songs.  Due to the nature of this song, it would be a core song if it was doing a decent amount of rune shielding.
<br />

<br />
So make this core song weak and it goes to the back of the book.  Make it work and it gets used 100% of the time.  Unfortunately Sony went the make it a crap song route in fear of it being an unbalanced one.  If this is the case, then it is just plain stupid to even think of giving us a song that in order to be usefull... it is unballancing!  (to Sony at least)
<br />

<br />
Gimping this down to what is does now is a waste of a precious song that might have been a usefull one in this expansion.
<br />

<br />
The freakshow of riz upgrades is another case of this.  The end upgrade is decent...the crap filler in the middle is for the bulk of the bards to tool around with.  If all bards has 30%-30% sony would have a heart attack.  
<br />

<br />
We can make such a difference to a group.  If Sony made our songs better, maybe the fear is that groups become &quot;We need a bard to be good groups&quot; kind of like at PoP release.  They have swung too far the other direction, to the point of making some feel like living in the past...reaching 60 and never going further.
<br />

<br />
Throw us a bone Sony, and make this expansion have some songs that increase our usefullness to more than it was at lv 65.  All clases get better so we add the same benifits to a group of uber 70s....yeah well the 60 bard nearly does the same benifit to that group as the 70...this is where it falls apart.
<br />

<br />
Having a 70 Bard should be of a decent benifit over having a 65 in your group....not just having a bard with 500 more hps.  This is broken at the moment.  (one day you get the end riz song and the mez73....well that just is not enough bud)  
<br />

<br />
We can pull just fine without 73 mez in this expansion due to mob placements...lots of classes are pulling...and if you need to mez a bunch of 73s in camp...someone screwed up in the first place.  nice song , but not a must have...just a bit more work.
<br />

<br />
Moose</span></td>
